        "timestamp": "2020-06-11 13:07:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1\n\nUpdated with full list of plugins, including those moved from the CCSDK repo.\nThis version of the CM container should be compatible with the Frankfurt version of the bootstrap container (1.12.6).  This container and the bootstrap both install plugins at deployment time, but they don't conflict with each other.  Using the Frankfurt version of the bootstrap container means that Frankfurt versions of blueprints will find the plugin versions that they need.\nOnce the blueprints are updated, the bootstrap container can be updated to eliminate plugin installation.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
